up of Monuments at</small> <a href="/wiki/Pattadakal" title="Pattadakal">Pattadakal</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Humayun%27s_Tomb" title="Humayun's Tomb">Humayun's Tomb</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kaziranga_National_Park" title="Kaziranga National Park">Kaziranga National Park</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Keoladeo_National_Park" title="Keoladeo National Park">Keoladeo National Park</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Khajuraho" title="Khajuraho">Khajuraho</a> <small>Group of Monuments</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Mahabodhi_Temple" title="Mahabodhi Temple">Mahabodhi Temple</a> <small>Complex at Bodh Gaya</small></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Manas_National_Park" title="Manas National Park">Manas Wildlife Sanctuary</a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Mountain_railways_of_India" title="Mountain railways of India">Mountain railways of India</a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Nanda_Devi_National_Park" title="Nanda Devi National Park">Nanda Devi</a> <small>and</small> <a href="/wiki/Valley_of_Flowers_National_Park" title="Valley of Flowers National Park">Valley of Flowers</a> <small>National Parks</small></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Qutb_complex" title="Qutb complex">Qutub Minar</a> <small>and its Monuments</small></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Red_Fort" title="Red Fort">The Red Fort complex</a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Bhimbetka_rock_shelters" title="Bhimbetka rock shelters">Rock Shelters of Bhimbetka</a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Konark_Sun_Temple" title="Konark Sun Temple">Sun Temple at Konark</a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sundarbans_National_Park" title="Sundarbans National Park">Sundarbans National Park</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><strong class="selflink">Taj Mahal</strong></span></p>
